high_descs: Turn left and head through the hallway with the white tile, all the way to the cabinet at the end.
Open the cupboard on the right and remove the tomato inside.
Leave this path the way you came in and take the first left, then left again and right into the sink.
Place the tomato in the sink in the bathroom.
Leave the bathroom and head back to the room you began in, going to the fridge on the left after entering.
Remove the tomato from the fridge.
Return to the bathroom where you placed the first tomato in the sink.
Place the second tomato into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place two Tomatoes in a SinkBasin.

Put the tomato into the sink.
